---
// SEOContent.astro
---

<section
  class="py-24 bg-surface border-y border-border/40 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-24">
      <!-- Title / Sticky Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 relative">
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-32">
          <p
            class="font-body text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand mb-6"
          >
            The Studio
          </p>
          <h2
            class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-ink font-normal tracking-tight mb-8"
          >
            Elevating the Art of Bridal Mehndi
          </h2>
          <a
            href="/book"
            class="hidden lg:inline-flex items-center gap-4 text-ink font-body text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:text-brand transition-colors"
          >
            Book Your Appointment
            <svg
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1"
            >
              <path d="M5 12H19M19 12L12 5M19 12L12 19" stroke-linecap="square"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Editorial Content Columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 prose-container relative">
        <!-- Always Visible Sections (1 and 4) -->
        <div class="columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-12 md:gap-16">
          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <div class="mb-12 break-inside-avoid-column">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-4">
              Why Brides Choose Aakriti for Their Wedding Mehndi
            </h3>
            <p
              class="font-body text-[15px] font-light leading-relaxed text-ink-muted mb-4"
            >
              Your wedding day is one of the most photographed moments of your
              life. The mehndi on your hands will appear in every portrait,
              every candid shot, every video reel your family passes around for
              years. That's not pressure - that's why it matters to get it
              right.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-body text-[15px] font-light leading-relaxed text-ink-muted"
            >
              Aakriti is a professional bridal mehndi artist with over 8 years
              of experience creating intricate, personalised henna designs for
              brides, families, and special occasions. Every design is crafted
              by hand, rooted in tradition, and tailored to the individual - not
              copied from a template.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <div class="mb-12 break-inside-avoid-column">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-4">
              What Makes a Mehndi Artist Worth Trusting
            </h3>
            <p
              class="font-body text-[15px] font-light leading-relaxed text-ink-muted mb-4"
            >
              Experience matters. So does the quality of the henna paste, the
              steadiness of the hand, and the ability to work efficiently
              without sacrificing detail. Over 8 years of practice means Aakriti
              has applied mehndi across hundreds of weddings, engagements, and
              family events. That repetition builds a precision that's visible
              in the final result.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-body text-[15px] font-light leading-relaxed text-ink-muted"
            >
              The paste used is natural, skin-safe, and formulated for deep,
              long-lasting colour. Aftercare guidance is provided with every
              appointment so your mehndi develops to its full richness.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
